{"about_the_game":"Experience the brutal and gruesome reality of the 19th Century with the <strong>Blood &amp; Gore DLC</strong> for <i>Battle Cry of Freedom</i>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306940/extras/tenor_3.gif?t=1678375176\" /><br><br>The DLC brings a new level of realism with <strong>improved death and wounded animations</strong>, including <strong>decapitations </strong>and <strong>dismemberments</strong>, as well as <strong>blood splatters</strong> and pools on the ground and walls. The DLC also includes new visual and audio effects, such as bloody or burned corpses, unique wounded animations and more. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306940/extras/tenor.gif?t=1678375176\" /><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>\u2022 Option for turning on/off gore.<br>\u2022 Decapitation with various melee weapons such as swords &amp; axes.<br>\u2022 Dismemberment with various melee weapons such as swords &amp; axes.<br>\u2022 Dismemberment with artillery shells and explosions.<br>\u2022 Blood splats and pools on terrain as well as surrounding geometry.<br>\u2022 Blood on corpses. <br>\u2022 Burned corpses. <br>\u2022 Unique wounded animations with their own blood particle effects. <br>\u2022 Unique wounded sounds and effects.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1678375176","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306940/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1678375176","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1678375176","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1678375176","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Onl